<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <title>Gestión de Plantillas WhatsApp - Sistema Médico</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet"/>

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary:       #135bec;
      --primary-light: #e8effd;
      --primary-dark:  #0d44c0;
      --body-bg:       #f0f2f8;
      --card-bg:       #ffffff;
      --border:        #e4e7ef;
      --text-muted:    #8891a5;
      --text-dark:     #1a2035;
      --green:         #16a34a;
      --green-light:   #dcfce7;
      --wa-header:     #075e54;
      --wa-bg:         #e5ddd5;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--body-bg);
      color: var(--text-dark);
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── Layout wrapper ── */
    .app-shell {
      display: flex;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
    }


    /* ══════════════════════════════
       TEMPLATE LIST PANEL
    ══════════════════════════════ */
    .template-list {
      width: 280px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .template-list-header {
      padding: 20px 16px 12px;
    }

    .template-list-header h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0;
    }


    .template-items {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .template-items::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
    .template-items::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 10px; }

    .template-item {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .15s;
    }

    .template-item:hover { background: var(--body-bg); }

    .template-item.active {
      background: var(--primary-light);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
    }

    .template-item .t-id {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .template-item.active .t-id { color: var(--primary); }
    .template-item:not(.active) .t-id { color: var(--text-muted); }

    .template-item h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      color: var(--text-dark);
    }

    .template-item p {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin: 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    /* ══════════════════════════════
       EDITOR SECTION
    ══════════════════════════════ */
    .editor-section {
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
      background: var(--body-bg);
    }

    .editor-section::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }
    .editor-section::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 10px; }

    .editor-topbar {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 0 28px;
      height: 64px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .editor-topbar h2 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .badge-active {
      background: var(--green-light);
      color: var(--green);
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      margin-left: 10px;
    }

    .btn-cancel {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: #64748b;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 7px 18px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .15s;
    }

    .btn-cancel:hover { background: var(--body-bg); }

    .btn-save {
      background: var(--primary);
      border: none;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 8px 22px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(19,91,236,.25);
      transition: background .15s, box-shadow .15s;
    }

    .btn-save:hover {
      background: var(--primary-dark);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(19,91,236,.35);
    }

    /* ── Form card ── */
    .form-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .form-label-custom {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      display: block;
    }

    .form-control-custom {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .form-control-custom:focus {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(19,91,236,.12);
    }

    .form-control-custom[readonly] {
      background: var(--body-bg);
      color: var(--text-muted);
      cursor: not-allowed;
    }

    /* Message editor toolbar */
    .msg-toolbar {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      background: var(--body-bg);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    .var-pill {
      padding: 3px 10px;
      background: var(--primary-light);
      color: var(--primary);
      border: 1px solid rgba(19,91,236,.2);
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .15s;
    }

    .var-pill:hover { background: rgba(19,91,236,.2); }

    .toolbar-divider {
      width: 1px; height: 20px;
      background: var(--border);
      margin: 0 2px;
    }

    .msg-body {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .msg-body textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      resize: none;
      padding: 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.7;
      outline: none;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .char-count {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    /* Action button card */

    /* ══════════════════════════════
       PHONE PREVIEW
    ══════════════════════════════ */
    .preview-label {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .phone-frame {
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 300px;
      border: 8px solid #1a2035;
      border-radius: 44px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.18), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
      background: #fff;
      position: relative;
    }

    .phone-notch {
      background: #1a2035;
      height: 24px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .phone-notch-inner {
      width: 72px; height: 14px;
      background: #111;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .wa-header {
      background: var(--wa-header);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .wa-header .bi { font-size: 18px; }

    .wa-avatar {
      width: 34px; height: 34px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wa-avatar img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    .wa-info { flex: 1; }
    .wa-info .wa-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
    .wa-info .wa-status { font-size: 9px; opacity: .8; margin: 0; }

    .wa-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
    .wa-actions .bi { font-size: 16px; }

    .wa-chat-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      height: 400px;
    }

    .wa-body {
      background: var(--wa-bg);
      padding: 10px;
      flex: 1;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }

    .wa-body::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 3px; }
    .wa-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(0,0,0,.15); border-radius: 10px; }
    .wa-body::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }

    .wa-input {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 8px;
      background: var(--wa-bg);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wa-date {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #5c6b6e;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 0 auto 10px;
      display: block;
      width: fit-content;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .wa-bubble {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 0 12px 12px 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      max-width: 92%;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .wa-bubble-meta {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 3px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .wa-bubble-meta span { font-size: 9px; color: #aaa; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .wa-bubble-meta .bi { font-size: 12px; color: #4fc3f7; }


    .wa-input-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 7px 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
    }

    .wa-input-box span {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #aaa;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .wa-input-box .bi { font-size: 16px; color: #aaa; }

    .wa-mic {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      background: #128c7e;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .wa-mic .bi { font-size: 16px; color: #fff; }

    .hint-text {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-style: italic;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-shell">


  <!-- ═══ TEMPLATE LIST ═══ -->
  <div class="template-list">
    <div class="template-list-header">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-3">
        <h2>Plantillas</h2>
        <button class="btn p-1 rounded-circle" style="color:var(--primary)">
          <i class="bi bi-plus-circle"></i>
        </button>
      </div>


    </div>

    <div class="template-items">
      <div class="template-item active">
        <p class="t-id">WABA-001</p>
        <h3>Recordatorio de Cita</h3>
        <p>Hola {{Nombre_Paciente}}, te recordamos...</p>
      </div>
      <div class="template-item">
        <p class="t-id">WABA-002</p>
        <h3>Promoción Blanqueamiento</h3>
        <p>¡Sonrisa perfecta! Aprovecha el 20%...</p>
      </div>
      <div class="template-item">
        <p class="t-id">WABA-003</p>
        <h3>Seguimiento Post-Op</h3>
        <p>Hola, ¿Cómo te sientes después de...</p>
      </div>
      <div class="template-item">
        <p class="t-id">WABA-004</p>
        <h3>Confirmación de Pago</h3>
        <p>Hemos recibido tu pago por el...</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══ EDITOR ═══ -->
  <div class="editor-section">
    <!-- Top Bar -->
    <div class="editor-topbar">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
        <h2>Editar Plantilla</h2>
        <span class="badge-active">Activa</span>
      </div>
      <div class="d-flex gap-2">
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content grid -->
    <div class="container-fluid px-4 py-4">
      <div class="row g-4">

        <!-- FORM -->
        <div class="col-12 col-xl-7">
          <div class="form-card mb-4">
            <div class="row g-3 mb-3">
              <div class="col-6">
                <label class="form-label-custom">Clave de Plantilla</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control-custom" value="WABA-001" readonly/>
              </div>
              <div class="col-6">
                <label class="form-label-custom">Tipo de Mensaje</label>
                <select class="form-control-custom">
                  <option>Servicio / Utilidad</option>
                  <option>Marketing</option>
                  <option>Autenticación</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3">
              <label class="form-label-custom">Nombre Descriptivo</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control-custom" value="Recordatorio de Cita"/>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                <label class="form-label-custom mb-0">Cuerpo del Mensaje</label>
                <span class="char-count">142 / 1024 caracteres</span>
              </div>

              <div class="msg-toolbar">
                <button class="var-pill">{{Nombre_Paciente}}</button>
                <button class="var-pill">{{Fecha_Cita}}</button>
                <button class="var-pill">{{Hora_Cita}}</button>
                <button class="var-pill">{{Nombre_Doctor}}</button>
                <div class="toolbar-divider"></div>
                <button class="btn p-1 rounded" style="line-height:1">
                  <i class="bi bi-emoji-smile" style="font-size:18px;color:var(--text-muted)"></i>
                </button>
              </div>

              <div class="msg-body">
                <textarea rows="8">Hola {{Nombre_Paciente}}, te recordamos que tienes una cita programada para el día {{Fecha_Cita}} a las {{Hora_Cita}} con el {{Nombre_Doctor}}.

Por favor, confirma tu asistencia respondiendo a este mensaje o cancela con al menos 24 horas de anticipación.

¡Te esperamos!</textarea>
              </div>
              <p class="hint-text mt-2">Los campos entre llaves {{ }} se sustituirán automáticamente con la información del paciente.</p>
              <div class="d-flex justify-content-end gap-2 mt-3">
                <button class="btn-cancel">Cancelar</button>
                <button class="btn-save">Guardar Cambios</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- PREVIEW -->
        <div class="col-12 col-xl-5">
          <div class="sticky-top" style="top:80px">
            <p class="preview-label">Vista Previa en Tiempo Real</p>

            <div class="phone-frame">
              <div class="phone-notch">
                <div class="phone-notch-inner"></div>
              </div>

              <!-- WA Header -->
              <div class="wa-header">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i>
                <div class="wa-avatar">
                  <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBuQpStgmNfCI0BOxJiodKnhoCTNr0lbqNJ_deFyGPOkRLgd60AJ63K_7QnZuXcmlNFqzJpraFTAiLm1VJfBJpyO8sv-Pr4DoRUp1GNES7X5U5T_6mCtUm4h0M1xG8wZkTIExqGW6j0U_SqBddoKuZ5nPV0PwXFtob0vHDlOQbfh5Id_tExevPo6IIyF2aFxkDu8IcggiwsLyGKHtd0uxEY4RSz5zHqtVNiieqqsqis1CSVM-c7sl1lTnNNvq0SUb2lWgbue5FyyLYw" alt="Clínica Dental Médica"/>
                </div>
                <div class="wa-info">
                  <p class="wa-name">Clínica Dental Médica</p>
                  <p class="wa-status">en línea</p>
                </div>
                <div class="wa-actions">
                  <i class="bi bi-camera-video"></i>
                  <i class="bi bi-telephone"></i>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- WA Chat wrapper -->
              <div class="wa-chat-wrapper">
              <!-- WA Chat -->
              <div class="wa-body">
                <div class="wa-date">HOY</div>

                <div class="wa-bubble">
                  Hola <strong>Juan Pérez</strong>, te recordamos que tienes una cita programada para el día <strong>15 de Octubre</strong> a las <strong>10:30 AM</strong> con el <strong>Dr. Alejandro M.</strong>.
                  <br/><br/>
                  Por favor, confirma tu asistencia respondiendo a este mensaje o cancela con al menos 24 horas de anticipación.
                  <br/><br/>
                  ¡Te esperamos!
                  <div class="wa-bubble-meta">
                    <span>11:05 AM</span>
                    <i class="bi bi-check2-all"></i>
                  </div>
                </div>


              </div><!-- /wa-body -->

              <!-- Input fijo abajo -->
              <div class="wa-input">
                <div class="wa-input-box">
                  <i class="bi bi-emoji-smile"></i>
                  <span>Mensaje</span>
                  <i class="bi bi-paperclip"></i>
                  <i class="bi bi-camera"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="wa-mic">
                  <i class="bi bi-mic"></i>
                </div>
              </div>
              </div><!-- /wa-chat-wrapper -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- Bootstrap 5 JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>